---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import LessonNav from '../../components/LessonNav.astro';
import LessonAudio from '../../components/LessonAudio.astro';
---
<Layout title="Lesson 6: CAD & Technical Drawings">
  <div class="lesson-header">
    <span class="lesson-badge">Lesson 6</span>
    <h1>CAD & Technical Drawings</h1>
    <p class="lesson-subtitle">Tips for using CAD to strengthen your Engineering Portfolio.</p>
    <LessonAudio slug="lesson-5" />
  </div>

  <p>
    Computer-Aided Design (CAD) is a great way to document your robot's design. 
    Here's how to use it well in your portfolio.
  </p>

  <h2>Why CAD Matters</h2>
  <p>CAD demonstrates:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Planning</strong>: You thought through the design before building</li>
    <li><strong>Precision</strong>: Exact measurements and specifications</li>
    <li><strong>Iteration</strong>: Changes made throughout the season</li>
    <li><strong>Communication</strong>: Clear visual representation of your robot</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Types of CAD Views</h2>
  <div class="view-grid">
    <div class="view-card">
      <div class="view-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 16V8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16z"></path><polyline points="3.27 6.96 12 12.01 20.73 6.96"></polyline><line x1="12" y1="22.08" x2="12" y2="12"></line></svg></div>
      <h4>Isometric Views</h4>
      <p>Overall robot from an angled perspective. Great for full robot overviews and assemblies.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="view-card">
      <div class="view-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><line x1="8" y1="12" x2="16" y2="12"></line><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="16"></line><line x1="9.17" y1="14.83" x2="14.83" y2="9.17"></line><line x1="14.83" y1="14.83" x2="9.17" y2="9.17"></line></svg></div>
      <h4>Exploded Views</h4>
      <p>Show how components fit together. Useful for assembly order and highlighting parts.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="view-card">
      <div class="view-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2v20"></path><path d="M2 12h8"></path><path d="M14 12h8"></path><path d="M7 7l5 5-5 5"></path><path d="M17 7l-5 5 5 5"></path></svg></div>
      <h4>Cross-Sections</h4>
      <p>Cut through to show internal components like motor placement and gear ratios.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="view-card">
      <div class="view-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m21.73 18-8-14a2 2 0 0 0-3.48 0l-8 14A2 2 0 0 0 4 21h16a2 2 0 0 0 1.73-3Z"></path><path d="M12 9v4"></path><path d="M12 17h.01"></path></svg></div>
      <h4>Orthographic</h4>
      <p>Standard engineering views (top, front, side) for dimensional accuracy.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2>Best Practices for CAD Screenshots</h2>
  <ol>
    <li><strong>High quality renders</strong>: Use good lighting and shadows</li>
    <li><strong>Hide unnecessary parts</strong>: Focus on what matters</li>
    <li><strong>Add annotations</strong>: Label key components</li>
    <li><strong>Use consistent colors</strong>: Same part = same color across images</li>
    <li><strong>Include scale</strong>: Add dimensions or reference objects</li>
  </ol>

  <h2>CAD Page Layout Example</h2>
  <p>Here's how a typical CAD page might look in your portfolio:</p>

  <div class="layout-example">
    <div class="layout-page">
      <div class="layout-header">
        <div class="layout-title-block"></div>
        <div class="layout-page-num">pg. 5</div>
      </div>
      <div class="layout-body">
        <div class="layout-main-img">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" class="layout-icon"><path d="M21 16V8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16z"/><polyline points="3.27 6.96 12 12.01 20.73 6.96"/><line x1="12" y1="22.08" x2="12" y2="12"/></svg>
          <span class="layout-placeholder">Full Robot CAD &mdash; Isometric View</span>
        </div>
        <div class="layout-row">
          <div class="layout-sub-img">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" class="layout-icon"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/><path d="M19.4 15a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 .33 1.82l.06.06a2 2 0 1 1-2.83 2.83l-.06-.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.82-.33 1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1 1.51V21a2 2 0 0 1-4 0v-.09"/></svg>
            <span class="layout-placeholder sm">Drivetrain</span>
          </div>
          <div class="layout-sub-img">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" class="layout-icon"><polygon points="13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2"/></svg>
            <span class="layout-placeholder sm">Arm Detail</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="layout-caption-lines">
          <div class="layout-caption-dot"></div>
          <div class="layout-line w100"></div>
          <div class="layout-line w80"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="layout-text-lines">
          <div class="layout-line w100"></div>
          <div class="layout-line w90"></div>
          <div class="layout-line w60"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="layout-annotations">
      <div class="layout-note">
        <span class="layout-dot"></span>
        Large hero CAD render dominates the top half
      </div>
      <div class="layout-note">
        <span class="layout-dot"></span>
        Detail views focus on specific subsystems
      </div>
      <div class="layout-note">
        <span class="layout-dot"></span>
        Captions label what judges are looking at
      </div>
      <div class="layout-note">
        <span class="layout-dot"></span>
        Brief body text explains design rationale
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2>Show Your CAD Evolution</h2>
  <div class="evolution">
    <div class="evo-stage">
      <span class="evo-label">Early Season</span>
      <h4>Version 1</h4>
      <ul>
        <li>Initial concept</li>
        <li>Basic prototype</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="evo-arrow">→</div>
    <div class="evo-stage">
      <span class="evo-label">Mid Season</span>
      <h4>Version 2</h4>
      <ul>
        <li>Refined after testing</li>
        <li>Added finer details</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="evo-arrow">→</div>
    <div class="evo-stage">
      <span class="evo-label">Competition</span>
      <h4>Version 3</h4>
      <ul>
        <li>Current design</li>
        <li>All hardware modeled</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2>Common CAD Mistakes</h2>
  <div class="mistakes-grid">
    <div class="mistake">
      <span class="icon">❌</span>
      <p>Low-resolution screenshots that look pixelated when printed</p>
    </div>
    <div class="mistake">
      <span class="icon">❌</span>
      <p>Cluttered images with too many parts visible</p>
    </div>
    <div class="mistake">
      <span class="icon">❌</span>
      <p>Missing dimensions or annotations for clarity</p>
    </div>
    <div class="mistake">
      <span class="icon">❌</span>
      <p>Only showing final design (not iterations)</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <LessonNav 
    prev={{ title: "Design Process", href: "/lessons/lesson-3/" }}
    next={{ title: "Robot Subsystems & Technical Pages", href: "/lessons/lesson-6/" }}
  />
</Layout>

<style>
  .view-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }

  .view-card {
    padding: 1.25rem;
    background: var(--bg-surface-solid);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  }

  .view-icon {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .view-card h4 {
    margin: 0 0 0.35rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-heading);
  }

  .view-card p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .evolution {
    display: flex;
    align-items: stretch;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
    overflow-x: auto;
  }

  .evo-stage {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    background: var(--bg-surface-solid);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    min-width: 160px;
  }

  .evo-label {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem;
    background: var(--accent-faint);
    color: var(--accent);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    border-radius: 4px;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .evo-stage h4 {
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text-heading);
  }

  .evo-stage ul {
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: 1.1rem;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
  }

  .evo-arrow {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .mistakes-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }

  .mistake {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.06);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  }

  .mistake .icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .mistake p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .view-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .mistakes-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .evolution {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .evo-arrow {
      transform: rotate(90deg);
      justify-content: center;
    }
  }

  /* Layout Example */
  .layout-example {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
    margin: 1rem 0 2rem;
  }
  .layout-page {
    flex: 0 0 260px;
    background: var(--bg-surface-solid);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    padding: .75rem;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    aspect-ratio: 8.5 / 11;
  }
  .layout-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: .5rem;
  }
  .layout-title-block {
    width: 60%;
    height: 8px;
    background: var(--accent);
    border-radius: 4px;
  }
  .layout-page-num {
    font-size: .6rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }
  .layout-body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: .5rem;
  }
  .layout-main-img {
    height: 110px;
    background: var(--accent-faint);
    border: 1px dashed var(--border-accent);
    border-radius: 6px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.25rem;
  }
  .layout-icon {
    color: var(--accent);
    opacity: 0.6;
  }
  .layout-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: .4rem;
  }
  .layout-sub-img {
    flex: 1;
    height: 60px;
    background: var(--accent-faint);
    border: 1px dashed var(--border-accent);
    border-radius: 4px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.15rem;
  }
  .layout-placeholder {
    font-size: .55rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-align: center;
    padding: .25rem;
  }
  .layout-placeholder.sm {
    font-size: .5rem;
  }
  .layout-caption-lines {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: .3rem;
    margin-top: .1rem;
  }
  .layout-caption-dot {
    width: 5px;
    height: 5px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--accent);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .layout-text-lines {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: .25rem;
    margin-top: .15rem;
  }
  .layout-line {
    height: 4px;
    background: var(--bg-surface-hover);
    border-radius: 2px;
  }
  .layout-line.w100 { width: 100%; }
  .layout-line.w90  { width: 90%; }
  .layout-line.w80  { width: 80%; }
  .layout-line.w60  { width: 60%; }
  .layout-annotations {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: .65rem;
    padding-top: .5rem;
  }
  .layout-note {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: .5rem;
    font-size: .85rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }
  .layout-dot {
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--accent);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 500px) {
    .layout-example {
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    .layout-page {
      flex: none;
      width: 100%;
      aspect-ratio: auto;
    }
  }
</style>
